to flash it with new firmware:

mv ~/Downloads/esp8266-20190529-v1.11.bin .
esptool.py --port /dev/cu.SLAB_USBtoUART erase_flash
esptool.py --port /dev/cu.SLAB_USBtoUART --baud 460800 write_flash --flash_size=detect 0 esp8266-20190529-v1.11.bin 

connect like:

$ screen -L /dev/cu.SLAB_USBtoUART 115200 -L 

^A^D to disconnect

^ADD to detach and disconnect


then screen -r to re-attach

ampy -p /dev/cu.SLAB_USBto_UART ls
ampy -p /dev/cu.SLAB_USBto_UART put main.py
ampy -p /dev/cu.SLAB_USBto_UART reset


to stop it, attach then:
import os
os.remove('main.py')
or
or.rename('main.py', 'old_main.py')


== relays:
Adafruit Non-Latching Mini Relay FeatherWing PRODUCT ID: 2895  https://www.adafruit.com/product/2895


